text: Mulegns was a municipality of the district Albula in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2016, the former municipalities of Mulegns, Bivio, Cunter, Marmorera, Riom-Parsonz, Salouf, Savognin, Sur and Tinizong- Rona merged into the new municipality of Surses.
